AI Usage Journal
Kindness Harbor
Kharbor@terpmail.umd.edu
One day, I decided to use artificial intelligence to assist me in planning my day because I was overwhelmed with tasks that I had to accomplish.
ChatGPT assisted me in creating a list of my assignments, my tasks, and deadlines so that all of my tasks were reflected in a single place.
While I utilized the capabilities of the AI to assist with considering what needed to be accomplished before moving forward, the decisions regarding how my day was to be organized and what could actually be accomplished rested with me.
I have not utilized the AI technology to perform or make decisions on my assignments.
However, I also attempted to inquire the AI on how it is possible to break down larger tasks into smaller steps, in order not to feel
At the end of the day, I felt less stressful and more focused since I had a clear plan as opposed to having everything in my head.
